:

1. *Blizini* je poznato da utiče na stanje našeg uma. (Being close is known to affect our state of mind.) 
2. U *blizini* njegovog doma je malo parkić. (Near his house there is a small park.)
3. On je želeo da živi u *blizini* prirode. (He wanted to live close to nature.)
4. Pokušala je da se skloni u *blizini* njegovog stana. (She tried to hide near his apartment.)
5. On je otišao u *blizinu* mora. (He went to the seaside.)